# --- Local working/scratch (not part of the deliverable) ---
# Build scratch, scratch notebooks, and any local archive live OUTSIDE this repo (in d:/tmp),
# but guard against accidental copies landing here:
_archive*/
*_backup.ipynb
scratch/
tmp/

# NOTE: eda_figs/ IS tracked on purpose. It holds the four interactive-figure PNG
# fallbacks that notebook.ipynb exports (the matplotlib panels render inline in the
# .ipynb itself). They are regenerated on every full execution.
